author: lundblad
msg: Locking branch: Implement locking semantics for commit in ra_local.
* subversion/include/svn_ra.h (svn_ra_plugin_t): Clarify life-times for
get_commit_editor2.
* subversion/libsvn_ra_local/ra_plugin.c (cleanup_access): New function.
(get_username): Duplicate username into session pool.  Create a new
access context on each call.  Reorganize to make more readable.
(deltify_etc_baton): Add repos and lock_tokens fields.
(deltify_etc): Unlock paths in lock_tokens, if any.
(svn_ra_local__get_commit_editor2): New function, copied from
svn_ra_local__get_commit_editor.  Add lock tokens to callback baton.
Add lock tokens to access context.
(svn_ra_local__get_commit_editor): Wrap the above function.
(ra_local_plugin): Add svn_ra_local__get_commit_editor2.
